Feature: To Set days to auto delete files from Restore Section- Header Option Icon
  Scenario: To Set days to auto delete files from Restore Section - Header Option
    Given I launch chrome browser
    When I open Url "https://www.syncoffice.com/module-test-dashboard/dashboard"
    Then I Click on login button
    And I enter UserName "sarika.mishra@candytechnologies.in" And Password "123456"
    And I Click on Login
    And Click on Cloud
    Then Click on Resource
    And Click on Restore Icon Resource
    When Restore Drawer opens up then Enter the Days Cycle to Delete the Files
    Then Click on Save
    Then Verify



